title: Stuck on
lyrics:
Uli bunmyeong gat-eun haneul
Alae salgo issneun geo maj-ji?
Ma-eumman meog-eumyeon eonjedeunji
Mannajil su issneun geo maj-ji?
Samuchige nega geuliwo

Tteunnun-eulo bam-eul saewo

Achim-i oneun geu solie

Jeongsin chalyeo bomyeon



Nae mam-eun tto neoegelo

Dallyeogago iss-eo



Uli bunmyeong gat-eun haneul

Alae salgo issneun geo maj-ji?

Ma-eumman meog-eumyeon eonjedeunji

Mannajil su issneun geo maj-ji?



Soleum kkichil mankeum geuliwo

Nado naega wae ileoneunji

Iyulado jom algo sip-eo

Ileon wajung-edo



Nae mam-eun tto neoegelo

Dallyeogago iss-eo

Hansungando neoegeseo

Jayulowojil suga eobs-eo

Geuleol su eobs-eo



Nae ma-eum-eun tto neoegelo



I sungando neoegelo

Dallyeogago iss-eo

Dan ilbundo neoegeseo

Jayulowojil suga eobs-eo

Geuleol su eobs-eo
